FOUNDATION JOURNEY

EMPATHY & LEADERSHIP


The mission of Public Matters Lebanon is to invest in the power of young minds and hearts and to ignite their worlds with empathy nurtured with ethical leadership, holding their hands to become superheroes of change, armed with the ability to understand, connect, and inspire.


LEADERSHIP



We understand the transformative power of empathetic leadership and its positive influence on the path ahead. Leadership nourishes self-confidence, effective communication, critical thinking, and problem-solving abilities, all of which are indispensable in today's complex world.


Read More

EMPATHY



The importance of cultivating empathy at an early age is the milestone of building strong, caring, ethical and confident individuals.

But have you ever wondered which remarkable organ is responsible for this remarkable human quality?
